        "text": "We’ll use the Spanish *formaciòn* to avoid confusion with the another key term, ‘formations’. I adopt *formations* from Raymond Williams’ cultural materialist lexicon: \\[ [[Raymond Williams]] 1981] to refer to consciously organised movements and communities that have characteristic cultural identifications and modes.\n\n"
